{"tid":1992471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［天馬］行動在即，大量五毛出沒，目的為瓦解己方行動","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T20:00:20.000Z","uid":145847,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6eab4675516f11552d82bc726ff86948ab219169","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"大量五毛出沒屈鬼屈狗<br />\n質疑搞手係鬼係狗<br />\n<br />\n目的為<br />\n1.帶風向互相猜忌加劇陣營內部分歧<br />\n2.於行動開始前直接以風向瓦解行動 （成功例子：重光仔，仲差啲害我哋又小個手足）<br />\n3.以分歧減少行動人數，危害前線安全<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好中計，人多就係力量<br />\n五毛狗老母比狗屌<br />\n51見"},{"pid":"230c30f0966dcecc3f11453884d8c215cf93524d","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2625545dd84b4c25322ef50910930cc4ae915120","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e78fa8fbe58530b0de4b29b738e217aae43bffc7","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1fff7a1d4ecdd6fd053b9b04a1eccd58953173a4","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3fb2c6c8999f98d01c3271d0b5854b1e0a0b6f02","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1121f8e754a46345a4a840646ea2b7463c3b2e45","tid":1992471,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"267c05eff1f30971c38149c5a236ee2928ea1758","tid":1992471,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54b2567af7025e853e3ddd8d954efa0c79ba6a74","tid":1992471,"uid":14